title: Mech Front Assault: Tank Combat

creator: Luis Carlos Zardo
descriptionHtml:
Mech Front Assault is an action packed Real Time Strategy game or, RTS for short.

In MFA you take control of your invading Factory Ship and must build and command your army against an endless horde of mechanized enemy monstrosities.

The game is featured in full 3D and you control the battlefield from above.

Command your units through intricates background, avoid obstacles and traps, use your Tactical Points to your advantage, focus your attack, move your units to strategical positions, use points to heal damaged units or...

...send an devastating AIRSTRIKE against an enemy position.

Upgrade your units to face even more brutal enemies as you advance through the game (99+ levels are planned)

If the situation gets dire, reinforce your DEFENSES with turrets (soon to be introduced)



Release your units and conquer the battlefield

Command your troops to defend your territory

99+ Levels of action packed combat

5 different units
*gatling
*cannon
*Missile
*Laser
*EMP

title: Mech Front Assault: Tank RTS

creator: Luis Carlos Zardo
descriptionHtml:
Mech Front Assault is an action packed Real Time Strategy game or, RTS for short.

In MFA you take control of a invading force and must build and command your army against an endless horde of mechanized enemy monstrosities.

The game is featured in full 3D and you control the battlefield from above.

Command your units through intricates background, avoid obstacles and traps, use your Tactical Points to your advantage, focus your attack, move your units to strategical positions, use points to heal damaged units or...

...send an devastating AIRSTRIKE against an enemy position.

Upgrade your units to face even more brutal enemies as you advance through the game (99+ levels are planned)

If the situation gets dire, reinforce your DEFENSES with turrets (soon to be introduced)



Release your units and conquer the battlefield

Command your troops to defend your territory

99+ Levels of action packed combat

5 different units
